{"tid":1703984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉）輕鐵司機教路！輕鐵一無，好多大西北人就返唔到工！","createTime":"2019-11-10T13:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T22:30:32.000Z","uid":331059,"like":120,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"bb9c82b2237556926111ce8a8ea4e6de20d50326","tid":1703984,"uid":331059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再扑輕鐵既月台設施同售票機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， <br />\n<br />\n雖然對MTR黎講不痛不癢，但一部出入站機閒閒地都要成5000幾蚊架，<br />\n<br />\n呢啲售票增值機直頭皮幾野一部，唔好亂扑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pn8caRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPn8caRx.jpg&h=408795f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NUiQRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NUiQRx.jpg&h=5a29696e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但以上都係啲濕碎野，爛左都唔緊要，但以下既野真係唔好扑啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下既野真係唔好扑啊！<br />\n以下既野真係唔好扑啊！<br />\n以下既野真係唔好扑啊！會嚴重影響到輕鐵行車架！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係波口，輕鐵轉左定轉右都係靠佢架，<br />\n如果扑爆左波口隔離個箱，咁佢就冇得發左發右，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mi6xaRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMi6xaRG.jpg&h=d4b70edc&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n轉唔到方向對輕鐵黎講好嚴重架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍色呢舊野係一個信號接收器，基本上每個波口附近都一定有佢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGF9XwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGF9XwP.jpg&h=b1fb6b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢會將輕鐵掉落去既信號傳到去波口，從而控制波口發左定發右。 <br />\n如果扑爛左佢，收唔到輕鐵信號既話，波口就會唔識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n如果再扑爛埋波口隔離個箱，到時就連手動推波口都唔得，就好大獲架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n橙色呢舊同樣都係一個信號接收器，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2vepbS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2vepbS.jpg&h=c05cf0e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個同輕鐵有交匯既路口附近都會有佢。<br />\n輕鐵經過橙色盒既時候會掉信號落去，從而去攞路口既燈，<br />\n如果佢爛左既話，咁輕鐵每逢經過路口就會冇燈，<br />\n分分鐘真係搞到輕鐵大塞車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白色果舊同橙色盒係兩兄弟，負責用黎取消返過完既路面燈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enPF4bX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenPF4bX.jpg&h=3e1d69c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個係路面燈，一個係波口方向燈，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZeyELo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZeyELo.jpg&h=24ac5887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬萬唔好扑佢地呀，輕鐵冇左佢地真係行唔到車架。<br />\n求下各位連登仔高抬貴手，放過輕鐵。<br />\n<br />\n我都求下大家，真係唔好扑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"97417018bc8ef2f08b699605ac9e95b1f7cd56aa","tid":1703984,"uid":2156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"CHINA<br />\n- Completely withdraw extradition bill<br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry<br />\n- No riot labeling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nC.H.I.N.A.<br />\nFive demands Not one less"},{"pid":"1f7e110ed92f7021f30c22726a314644af68349f","tid":1703984,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"聽日警察分辨唔到罷工嘅人及準時返工嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0753f65efb1e3181948981608ace5ec859de1c53","tid":1703984,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我要番工 千祈唔好咁做!!!!!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MG7Hx4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMG7Hx4n.png&h=41866d85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=