ih.kg/1703752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽日可能出現嘅情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703148</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n驅逐共黨 光復香港"},{"pid":"1e6d5326c57453b1df81d400977ac8c94c290185","tid":1703984,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ae736dd9802707403c0000d6934e7fe4838d50","tid":1703984,"uid":220240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"612起到身，1111都要起到身"},{"pid":"d5d596c1af431f25e5075f37abb2010c09c33f24","tid":1703984,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59d1fa1b40e54eea7963829662ac6abe66517f4","tid":1703984,"uid":331059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"926de6affdd73d3cd53f401fed2ec6962d8d50e5","tid":1703984,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9138e24b681daaa1d304db57626b6744cb4b958","tid":1703984,"uid":20930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"波口位，唔好響尖軌位置用石仔搞到轉唔到方向呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電纜都係，響部分位置，有個可以切斷電源既開關，唔好亂拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA字係尖軌，一頂住就轉唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkrailway.org/hkr32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/